---
import Section from "../Section.astro";
---

<Section title="education and training" anchor="education">
  <div class="education_layout">
    <div class="education_intro">
      <p class="education_kicker">Formal background</p>
      <p class="education_text">
        Training across software engineering, distributed systems, and earlier
        technical studies that shaped a practical, systems-first mindset.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <article class="education_item">
        <h3>Software Engineering, UPM Madrid</h3>
        <p>
          I earned my degree in Software Engineering from UPM, Madrid. The program
          covered Unix systems, C++, Java, web development, Android applications,
          project management, agile methods, testing, and quality.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="education_item">
        <h3>Graduation Project and Internship</h3>
        <p>
          In my final year, I joined a group internship project where I developed
          a desktop application for refactoring source code after SQL query changes.
          That work became the basis for my graduation project.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="education_item">
        <h3>Master’s in Computer Engineering</h3>
        <p>
          I later completed a Master’s in Computer Engineering focused on
          Distributed Software and Services, with deeper study in cloud technologies,
          distributed systems, and a full-stack university internship.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="education_item">
        <h3>Technical Formation Before University</h3>
        <p>
          Before university, I completed a two-year program in Maintenance and
          Management of Industrial Equipment, with training in quality assurance,
          process management, planning, development, and testing.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>

<style>
  .education_layout {
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
  }
  .education_intro {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    max-width: 32rem;
  }
  .education_kicker {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .education_text {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 34ch;
  }
  .wrapper {
    text-align: left;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .education_item {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .education_item h3,
  .education_item p {
    margin: 0;
  }
  .education_item h3 {
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.8vw, 1.2rem);
    color: var(--text-main);
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }
  @media only screen and (min-width: 980px) {
    .education_layout {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.34fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      align-items: start;
      column-gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    }
    .wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    }
  }
</style>
